    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Cultural landscapes that are significant in the history of landscape architecture or gardening or that were developed as a result of historic use of natural features; includes shaped areas of land and sometimes structures.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
